text:
My high school video,
it seems like a fan found it...

Huh, that's...
Is there a problem?

Not really a problem...
It's just embarrassing!

Hmm... It's surprising
how even with just one video, it can be found...

.........
I don't think there's anything to be embarrassed about.

After all, it's because of that video
that you're here now, right?

Oh... yeah, thinking about it as the video that
led me to meet you, I guess I should cherish it...!

Well then, since we're here,
want to watch that video together now?
